"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/417149","Department for Business, Innovation and Skills","false","2015-09-15","<p>Meetings and attendance details for the Council for Science and Technology can be found here - <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/council-for-science-and-technology/about/our-governance" target="_blank">https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/council-for-science-and-technology/about/our-governance</a></p><p> </p>","Orpington","Joseph Johnson",,"2015-09-15T15:11:11.037Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/417149/answer","Biography information for Joseph  Johnson","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/417149/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/417149/answer",,,,,"26","Business, Innovation and Skills","Business, Innovation and Skills","2015-09-07","Council for Science and Technology","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Business, Innovation and Skills, on what dates the Council for Science and Technology met in the last 12 months; on what dates and who was in attendance at each such meeting.","false","Biography information for Chuka Umunna","Streatham","Mr Chuka Umunna","9285"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/417150","Department for Business, Innovation and Skills","false","2015-09-15","<p>The Newton Fund was launched in April 2014. In the first year of the fund (FY14/15) the following awards were made:</p><p>a) 287 Fellowships</p><p>b) 1164 other awards</p>","Orpington","Joseph Johnson",,"2015-09-15T15:47:59.193Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/417150/answer","Biography information for Joseph  Johnson","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/417150/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/417150/answer",,,,,"26","Business, Innovation and Skills","Business, Innovation and Skills","2015-09-07","Newton Fund","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Business, Innovation and Skills, how many (a) fellowships and (b) other outputs have been delivered under the Newton Fund in each of the last five years.","false","Biography information for Chuka Umunna","Streatham","Mr Chuka Umunna","9286"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/417151","Department for Business, Innovation and Skills","false","2015-09-14","<p>We required at least 19,000 businesses to complete a business needs assessment (either online or face-to-face) to provide robust evidence gathering under the programme. 27,117 businesses completed this assessment. There was no threshold set for the number of vouchers used.</p><p> </p>","Broxtowe","Anna Soubry",,"2015-09-14T09:28:30.853Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/417151/answer","Biography information for Anna Soubry","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/417151/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/417151/answer",,,,,"26","Business, Innovation and Skills","Business, Innovation and Skills","2015-09-07","Small Businesses: Advisory Services","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Business, Innovation and Skills, what threshold his Department set for the number of Growth Vouchers used to provide robust evidence-gathering under the programme.","false","Biography information for Chuka Umunna","Streatham","Mr Chuka Umunna","9276"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/417152","Department for Business, Innovation and Skills","false","2015-09-14","<p><strong> </strong></p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p>All unused funds have been redistributed across the department's other programmes to support business start-up and growth.</p><p> </p><p><strong> </strong></p><p> </p>","Broxtowe","Anna Soubry","9269","2015-09-14T09:19:59.053Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/417152/answer","Biography information for Anna Soubry","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/417152/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/417152/answer",,,,,"26","Business, Innovation and Skills","Business, Innovation and Skills","2015-09-07","Small Businesses: Advisory Services","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Business, Innovation and Skills, how he plans to spend the funds which were allocated but unused as part of the Growth Vouchers scheme.","false","Biography information for Chuka Umunna","Streatham","Mr Chuka Umunna","9277"
